<View style={{ flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center", padding: 5 }}>
    <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", alignItems: "center" }}>
        <Image
            source={images.GUARD}
            style={{
                width: 24,
                height: 24,
                borderRadius: 90,
                borderWidth: 1,
                borderColor: "#FFF",
                marginTop: 17,
                marginBottom: 17,
                marginRight: 11
            }}
        ></Image>
        <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ alignSelf: 'center', paddingVertical: 20 }}>Privacy And Security</Text>
    </View>
    <Image
        source={images.VECTOR}
        color="#292D32"
        style={{
            width: 5,
            height: 11,
            marginTop: 20,
            marginBottom: 20,
        }}
    ></Image>
</View>
